sql getstockgoods: SELECT *
				FROM MZ.BETAEMPIK_STOCK
				WHERE CODE_WARES IN (735177, 715319)
AND CODE_SHOP = '88' ORDER BY RANK_ESHOP DESC, QTY  DESC
